Global Quizzle

Overview

Global Quizzle is a simple C program that tests your knowledge of world geography through a multiple-choice quiz. Answer questions correctly to increase your score!

Features

Five multiple-choice questions about world geography

User-friendly input system

Automatic score calculation with feedback

How to Run

Clone or download this repository.

Open a terminal and navigate to the directory.

Compile the program using:

gcc global_quizzle.c -o quizzle

Run the program:

./quizzle

Example Questions

"Which is the largest continent?"

A) Africa

B) Asia

C) Europe

D) Australia

Contributing

Feel free to fork this repository and add more questions or features!

